   associated Al showed a similar sequence for all the localities,
   confirming a common daily pattern in soundscape organization. According
   to the way in which ECs are distributed along the 24 h, the first
   hundred more frequent ECs were aggregated into seven major patterns:
   some ECs have a dominant distribution around sunrise, whereas others
   prevail at midday or at night.
   EEDI provides a visual representation of each recording day (240 RMs) in
   an Euclidean space delimited by ACIf(t) (x), ACIf(t) evenness (y) and
